  <summary date="2024-08-14T18:00:59Z" status="Reported to Senate">Protecting Older Americans Act of 2023

This bill prohibits a predispute arbitration agreement or predispute joint-action waiver from being valid or enforceable if it requires arbitration of a dispute involving age discrimination.</summary>
